messages.message: This menu should be saying Edit project instead of Edit app
to edit the app, you are taken to the project

Then I am not editing the App, I am editing the Project, to edit the App I can only Publish or Create a Deployment so I really don't ever edit an App.  I edit a project to then potentially create or update an App

@Dale DeLoy we've collected a lot of similar feedback, we hear you! Here's some great research the PM and design team put together: https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/117S2fSe4AaGt22q0774dy9FB2bakaudSWu0w3p-iSWc/edit#slide=id.g28156511381_0_177

We probably won't make changes in the short term as we're figuring out the long-term plan to fix this stuff.
great to see this research!  I am not the only one getting confused by this
